CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three men, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence, shaking hands with other man, standing in the Office of the Mayor at the City County Building
